{"tid":942812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【所以話】的士司機被臭到不舉　性交易不成怒告台妹","createTime":"2018-12-16T05:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T07:20:42.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"794ad8520abe466dfd08e47c47050b6bdd0d496f","tid":942812,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"的士司機被臭到不舉　性交易不成怒告台妹<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/mobile/bkn-20181216010705865-1216_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181216%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181216010705865-1216_00952_001.html&d=CKAMKtmgZZ4JHF8XMmphFviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=18f7eeb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/mobile/bkn-20181216010705865-1216_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣新北市一名的士司機日前搭訕一名黃姓女子，以2000元（新台幣．下同，約500港元）價格換取黃女提供性服務。雙方談妥後到便利店廁所「交易」，未料司機聞到黃女身有異味，以「做不下去」為由要求黃女還錢，但對方卻藉機逃走，氣得司機將她告上法院。<br />\n<br />\n事發於去年12月10日，該名年約40歲的司機在便利店內搭訕黃女，黃女先向他借錢，但司機反要求黃女提供性服務，雙方談好以2000元為酬勞。但司機在撫摸親吻黃女時，突然聞到女方身上傳來惡臭，一問之下竟得知她已兩日沒洗澡，立即興趣全無，要求取消交易。<br />\n<br />\n但黃女未有還款而是趁機逃走，的士司機遂報警處置。台北地檢署表示，黃女確實與司機發生親密互動，是後來司機自己不舉致無法性交，即使黃女事後不還錢，也不能認定她詐騙，因此判黃女無罪，不將其起訴。"},{"pid":"df9fe4a51f4cbe119958d1e4ffc4ff71a188bf8f","tid":942812,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"台灣臭鮑魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb93b8721b94be326c1b7858dd7a3be3c7ff9f1","tid":942812,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"兩日無沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b2c92b9bedf12f7af4ca2cebab1d2da83c3724","tid":942812,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcyPK0m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcyPK0m.gif&h=468c1b46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31d9bdcfc28778ee7360a5121055b92172ef4a3e","tid":942812,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"臭閪"}]}